<p><span>Switzerland truly is a country of contrasts. Switzerland's stunning scenery includes snow-dusted mountain peaks, tranquil shimmering lakes, dramatic gorges and towering waterfalls. Whether you venture just outside of town or all the way up a mountain, exploring Switzerland’s natural treasures is sure to be a memorable experience. </span>But it's not just about the nature, because Switzerland's cultural offering and diverse food scene combine to create a truly memorable summer holiday.</p>
